General.Name: Inghams Group Limited
General.Description: Inghams Group Limited, together with its subsidiaries, produces and sells chicken and turkey products in Australia and New Zealand. The company provides frozen, gluten free, and ready to cook chicken and turkey products under the Ingham's brand name. It also offers stock feeds for poultry and pig industries. Inghams Group Limited was founded in 1918 and is based in North Ryde, Australia.
